{"tid":1683168,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港黑警，貪求無厭 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-10-30T13:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T13:43:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da521bc9db5b7d416a2a68ea25179f49d96f56fe","tid":1683168,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191030/20796133/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796133%2F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHiWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=aa90d784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796133%2F&h=7486fa82\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191030/20796133/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港黑警，貪求無厭 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191030/large/1572334212_0c05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191030%2Flarge%2F1572334212_0c05.jpg&h=5b1cfb6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港黑警威震全城，名浹海外，連臺灣內政部都聞風色變，發表公文曰：「有網路消息說，香港黑警將攜家眷大舉移居臺灣，並呼籲政府慎防。」除了防其暴，還要防其貪。<br />\n<br />\n黑警之貪，顯而易見者，是他們的體育遊樂會最近大肆擴充及裝修，所需三億元竟然要鐵路公司支付，當作沙中線鐵路建築費，而鐵路建築費一分一毫都是公帑。消防員和黑警同屬紀律部隊，民望更遠高於黑警，但其會所與黑警相比，簡直寒酸。<br />\n<br />\n又香港黑政府最近發表施政報告，宣布加速興建紀律部隊宿舍。按紀律部隊有消防、海關、入境、懲教、黑警等五支，興建的宿舍有二千三百八十三戶，黑警竟獨佔一千一百八十四戶。明貪已是如此，暗貪真不知如何。<br />\n<br />\n黑警除了在香港謀幸福，還謀及大陸房地產利潤。十月十七日，黑警員佐級協會主席林志偉致函同袍，說雅居樂集團計劃於肇慶興建香港城，協會將與之洽商，求以「最優惠價格」購買香港城樓房，以利同袍。協會外務長李耀廷說這不是恃勢謀私，廉政公署、公務員事務局等等當然不敢稍有異議。看來，黑警在香港買樓房，地產商也應予最優惠價格，報答保護之恩。<br />\n<br />\n古人說，「當失（失道）之時，君暗政亂，兵驕民困」（《新五代史》卷三十一）。今日香港在習近平主席指揮之下，固然開創了歷來最輝煌盛世，但古人的話真沒有錯。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"b443d9be13e74f3ba5773451f9fb9456785a1a79","tid":1683168,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /Task1</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHiWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=2dbd275b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"}]}